	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Probably a Legate under Antonius Creticus in Greece (SIG³ 748). C. Iulius (Caesar?) Pat. (20,131) Cos. 59, 48, 46-44, Pr. 62 Legate, probably under Antonius Creticus, in Greece, and probably in the latter part of 73 (SIG³ 748)." .
